	<h3>54. Bollinger Bands + RSI + ADX binary options strategy</h3>
	<p>Bollinger Bands + RSI + ADX binary options strategy is used only for time intervals:<br>
1.From 2am to 5am EST<br>
2.From 8am to 12am EST<br>
3.From 7:30pm to 10pm EST<br>
Also, in order to avoid loss, don't use this strategy 30 minutes before or one hour after the news announcement marked red or orange in the economic calendar!
Trading strategy description<br>
Trading assets: All the currency pairs<br>
Time frame: 1M<br>
Indicators used:<br>
1.Bollinger Bands (20, 2)<br>
2.RSI (7)<br>
</p>
	<img src="images/strategy/str110.jpg" height="" width="">
	<img src="images/strategy/str111.jpg" height="" width="">
	<p>Conditions required for buy options:<br>
1.The price rose above the upper band or fell below the lower Bollinger band<br>
2.The RSI rose above 70 or dropped below 30<br>
3.ADX readings do not exceed the value of 32<br>
Buy option CALL:<br>
1.The price is below the lower Bollinger band<br>
2.The RSI drops below 30<br>
3.ADX doesn't exceed the value 32<br>
	</p>
	<img src="images/strategy/str112.jpg" height="" width="">
	<p>Buy option PUT:<br>
1.The price is above the upper Bollinger band<br>
2.The RSI rose above 70<br>
3.ADX doesn't exceed the value 32<br>
	</p>
	<img src="images/strategy/str113.jpg" height="" width="">
	<p>Refrain from trading:<br>
1.When price touches the middle Bollinger band<br>
2.When price touches the opposite Bollinger band<br>
	</p>
